disappoint him?

305
00:16:14,517 --> 00:16:16,033
I refuse to die.

306
00:16:18,765 --> 00:16:22,592
Yes, I see. Well, surely
this rift isn't irreparable.

307
00:16:24,617 --> 00:16:28,203
