355
00:19:11,225 --> 00:19:12,423
Oh, my God.

356
00:19:13,338 --> 00:19:15,133
-You don't...
-Let me put it this way-

357
00:19:15,308 --> 00:19:17,733
I got a box of condoms
in my dresser.

358
00:19:17,887 --> 00:19:19,223
