359
00:19:19,426 --> 00:19:20,921
Can only account
for eight of 'em.

360
00:19:22,347 --> 00:19:24,681
How can you be so
calm about this?

361
00:19:25,025 --> 00:19:25,671
Edie?

362
00:19:26,238 --> 00:19:26,822
Yeah?

363
00:19:26,995 --> 00:19:29,370
Can you help me
with this tie? I...

364
