425
00:22:55,548 --> 00:22:57,711
People aren't gonna buy that,
so here's what I was thinking.

426
00:22:58,067 --> 00:22:59,721
I slap on one of those gowns,

427
00:23:00,027 --> 00:23:02,250
I play Tanya's "big sister",

