453
00:24:23,687 --> 00:24:24,503
Daddy!

454
00:24:24,757 --> 00:24:25,911
Hey, baby girl.

455
00:24:26,387 --> 00:24:27,462
That the guy?

456
00:24:27,807 --> 00:24:28,683
Yep!

457
